INSERT INTO `oc_information_description` VALUES (4,1,'About Us','&lt;p&gt;&lt;article class=&quot;uk-article&quot;&gt;\r\n\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Riding for less since 2006...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Omen\'s Shoes founded in 2006, was the first Greek online store of its\r\n kind. Since then we continue with a huge variety, over 100 brands and \r\nthousands of products. Streetwear, Sneakers, Snowwear, Beachwear, \r\nUnderwear, Snowboard, Skateboard and many other items, accessories and \r\nAction sports. Our passion for what we do, is our inspiration and our \r\naim an exceptional customer service.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;ride with us!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n&lt;/article&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','About Us','',''),(5,1,'Terms &amp; Conditions','&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1) Conditions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Company reserves the right to modify or update these terms and \r\nconditions of the transactions made ​​through e-shop, according to the \r\nneeds and usages.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The company undertakes to inform users of any changes and any changes through the website of this online store.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2) Provided information and Products&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Company is committed to the quality, completeness and validity of the\r\n information given on the website, both as to the exact details \r\ndescribed as those supplied by the online store, services, subject to \r\nany technical or typographical errors which cannot be predicted or occur\r\n unintentionally or downtime of the site on grounds of force majeure.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3) Limitation of Liability&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Company shall not be liable to customer / users for any damages resulting from the execution or order them.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Also reserves the delivery time of goods in cases of force majeure. \r\nNo guarantee can be provided for the availability of products, but we \r\nguarantee timely information to end consumers of their unavailability.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Company assumes no responsibility for any damages that may be \r\nincurred in transferring the products. The products traveling on behalf \r\nof and under the responsibility of the buyer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The online store provides the content (e.g. information, names, \r\nimages, illustrations, etc.), products and services available through \r\nthe website &quot;as is&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In any case, the online store of the Company is not responsible for \r\nany legal or civil or / and penal nature nor for any damage (direct, \r\nspecial or consequential which indicatively and not restrictively, \r\nalternatively or / and: loss of profits, data, lost profits, \r\ncompensation, etc.) from site visitors or third reason has to do with \r\nrunning or not and / or use of the site and / or failure to provide \r\nservices and / or information available from this and / or any \r\nunauthorized paid products and / or services and / or information \r\navailable through this.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4) Intellectual property&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This website is the official online store of individual enterprise \r\nSkateshop &amp;nbsp; VAT N. EL042175754. All site content, including pictures,\r\n graphics, photographs, drawings, texts, services and products are the \r\nintellectual property of the Company and protected by the relevant \r\nprovisions of Greek law, European law and international conventions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Any copying, analog / digital recording and mechanical reproduction, \r\ndistribution, transmission, downloading, processing, resale, create \r\nderivative works, or misleading the public about the real provider of \r\nthe content of the website. Any reproduction, republication, uploading, \r\nposting, or transmission or any other use of the Content in any manner \r\nor means, for commercial or other purposes is permitted only with prior \r\nwritten permission of the Company or any other legitimate holder of \r\nthose copyrights.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The names, images, logos and trademarks representing the Company and /\r\n or its online store and / or third parties affiliated with them and \r\ntheir products or services are exclusive trademarks and trademarks of \r\nthe Company and / or electronic office and / or more third parties and \r\nare protected by Greek, European and international trademark laws, and \r\nindustrial and intellectual property. In any event, occurrence, and \r\nreport on their website and online store should in no way be construed \r\nas a transfer or license or right to use them.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5) User Responsibility&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Users of the site www.skateshop.gr agree not to use the online store \r\nto send, post, send by e-mail or otherwise transmit any Content that is \r\nunlawful, harmful, threatening, abusive, harassing, defamatory, \r\nlibelous, vulgar, obscene, libelous, violate the privacy of another, \r\nshow empathy, or is racial, ethnic or other discrimination, may cause \r\nharm minors in any way, not be transmitted in accordance with the laws \r\nor administrative or contractual relationships (such as inside \r\ninformation, proprietary and confidential information learned or \r\ndisclosed as part of employment relationships or covered by \r\nconfidentiality agreements) infringes any patent, trademark, trade \r\nsecret, copyright or other proprietary rights of others, contains \r\nsoftware viruses or any other computer code, files or programs designed \r\nto interrupt, damage, destroy or equipment in any software or hardware, \r\nintentionally or unintentionally contravenes existing Greek and EU \r\nlegislation and provisions that may impede a third party in any way and \r\nany Content used to collect or store personal data about other users.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6) Security&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Company recognizes the importance of the issue of security of \r\nyour personal data and your online transactions and take all necessary \r\nmeasures with the most modern and advanced methods to ensure maximum \r\nsafety. All information related to your personal information and \r\ntransactions are secure and confidential. In addition, our online shop \r\nis certified to international safety certificates which are offered by \r\nthe collaboration with Eurobank.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7) Privacy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;When you visit the pages of www.skateshop.gr to order products, but \r\nalso to ensure that we can contact you to let you know about our new \r\nproducts, you will likely be asked to fill in your personal information \r\n(name, email address, etc.). Any personal data anywhere on the pages and\r\n services of this website are intended solely to ensure the operation of\r\n the service and may not be used by anyone, without complying with the \r\nprovisions of the law.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The online store operates in accordance with applicable Greek and EU \r\nlegislation and maintain security of your personal data for as long as \r\nyou are registered with a service which is deleted after the end of the \r\ntrading relationship. The personal data you store online used \r\nexclusively by or affiliated with this company, to support, promote and \r\nexecute the trading relationship.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The holdings data file may be notified to the competent judicial, \r\npolice and other legal authorities at their request and in accordance \r\nwith the pertinent laws.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8) Product Buy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Company makes every effort to provide high quality but \r\nnevertheless is not responsible for any errors in product prices and \r\nfeatures and cannot guarantee that there will be no downtime of the \r\nwebsite or &quot;human&quot; errors when updating / showing of a product. For \r\nsafety and efficiency of the markets where we invite you find that a \r\nproduct is offered at an unusually low or high price compared to its \r\nmarket value before submitting the order to contact us.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;9) Return Policy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Policy Changes and Returns detailed in the corresponding section.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;10) Cancel Order&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Your order listed for execution only after completing all the steps of the shopping cart and view the corresponding message.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If after completion you wish to cancel your order, you must contact us directly, either by telephone or contact form.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Orders already shipped can be returned after receiving them.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The cancellation policy detailed in Returns Policy section.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;11) Payment&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our payment methods are detailed in the corresponding section.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;12) Rates shop&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In any case, although we make every effort to accurately display the \r\ndata and the values ​​we present in our store we cannot exclude the \r\npossibility of occurrence of typographical or clerical errors in product\r\n prices and features.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All prices include VAT 24%.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;13) Shipping Costs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Your fees are detailed in section SHIPPING.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;14) Delay Order&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Your order may be delayed for the following reasons:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;i. The product you ordered is not available: Among the plethora of \r\nproducts that we expose in our online store there are rare cases where a\r\n product may not be available. In this case we will contact you to give \r\nyou all the alternatives.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;ii. In periods of extreme weather or strikes, and in any event of \r\nforce majeure, which may affect the transport and delivery of your order&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;iii. If it is impossible to telephone and / or e-mail (e-mail) \r\ncommunication with you (if a problem occurs on your order, or in \r\nconnection with the product or in relation to the payment of) because \r\ne.g. your information you entered is not correctly updated&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;15) Warranty&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The products covered by the warranty of their manufacturer. The \r\nwarranty will be considered by the company comply with the conditions \r\nset out by the manufacturer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','Terms &amp; Conditions','',''),(3,1,'Privacy Policy','&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Privacy Policy&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','Privacy Policy','',''),(6,1,'Delivery Information','&lt;br&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Greece &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;We&amp;nbsp;cooperate with the Geniki Tachydromiki Courier and delivery time \r\nis 1 - 2 working days. The shipping cost is at 3 €, regardless of the \r\nsize and weight of the order. On orders over 40 €, shipping is for FREE.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Cyprus &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;We cooperate with the DHL and the delivery time is 2 - 4 working \r\ndays. The shipping cost is at 9.90 € and orders over 100 € shipping is \r\nfor FREE.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Europe &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;We cooperate with the DHL and the delivery time is 2 - 4 working \r\ndays. The shipping cost is at 9.90 € and orders over 100 € shipping is for\r\n FREE.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Rest of the world&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;We work with the Greek Post and the delivery time is 1 - 2 weeks. The\r\n shipping cost is at 20 € (taxes and customs clearance are paid by the \r\ncustomer). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','Delivery Information','','');
